---
title: Chorizo Mac 'n' Cheese with Roasted Broccoli
description: Who doesn't love a classic mac 'n' cheese?! Gooey, cheesy, melty comfort! We've paired it with chorizo to add extra deliciousness and a crispy shallot topping for that desirable crunch and flavour. Roasted broccoli comes alongside, so that you can still get your greens in.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/macaroni-au-fromage-et-au-chorizo-9a444ba3.jpg
